title: Readit app for Reddit updated for Windows 10
text:
Readit app for Reddit updated for Windows 10 
Published By: WinSuperSite.com - Today 
Readit is a very popular third party app for Windows that allows app level access to Reddit. It has now been updated for Windows 10.
